{
  "info": {
    "name": "KongAir Workshop API",
    "description": "Colecci\u00f3n de Postman para probar el ejercicio final de consolidaci\u00f3n en la instancia local de Docker de Kong Gateway.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. GET /flights (App-External - Exitoso)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "apikey",
            "value": "external-secret-123",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "http://localhost:28000/flights",
          "protocol": "http",
          "host": [
            "localhost"
          ],
          "port": "28000",
          "path": [
            "flights"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Prueba exitosa. Consume la ruta `/flights` utilizando la key `external-secret-123` (App-External). Este consumidor pertenece al grupo `external` de ACL, por lo que tiene acceso permitido."
      },
      "response": [],
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "console.log('Iniciando request: App-External - Exitoso');",
              "pm.environment.set('request_start_time', Date.now());"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('Response time is less than 500ms', function () {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(500);",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. GET /flights (App-Internal - Denegado por ACL)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "apikey",
            "value": "internal-secret-123",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "http://localhost:28000/flights",
          "protocol": "http",
          "host": [
            "localhost"
          ],
          "port": "28000",
          "path": [
            "flights"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Prueba denegada. Consume la ruta `/flights` utilizando la key `internal-secret-123` (App-Internal). Este consumidor NO pertenece al grupo `external`, por lo que Kong deber\u00eda devolver un `403 Forbidden`."
      },
      "response": [],
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status code is 403 Forbidden', function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(403);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('Error message is correct', function () {",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.message).to.include('You cannot consume this service');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. GET /flights (Sin API Key - No Autorizado)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "http://localhost:28000/flights",
          "protocol": "http",
          "host": [
            "localhost"
          ],
          "port": "28000",
          "path": [
            "flights"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Prueba sin autenticaci\u00f3n. Al no enviar el header `apikey`, Kong deber\u00eda devolver un `401 Unauthorized`."
      },
      "response": [],
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status code is 401 Unauthorized', function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(401);",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. GET /get (HTTPBin - Transformaciones de Headers)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "http://localhost:28000/get",
          "protocol": "http",
          "host": [
            "localhost"
          ],
          "port": "28000",
          "path": [
            "get"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Prueba de transformaciones. Llama al endpoint libre `/get`. Revisa en la respuesta que el header `x-inter-env: lab` haya sido inyectado en el request por Kong hacia el upstream."
      },
      "response": [],
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "pm.test('Header x-inter-env was injected', function () {",
              "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.headers['X-Inter-Env']).to.eql('lab');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
